name: One Evening With Me at sunset

metadata.name: Pleased To Meet U
metadata.description:
When Alexandra sat down on the rock I asked her if she wanted to pass something on to the viewer.

She said, "Pleased to meet you!" And she laughed shyly.

Tell me, do you have the ability to look at a photo as if to bring it to life? 
If you've never done that, try looking into her eyes right now and imagine her saying those words...


"Pleased to meet you," 1/1 NFTs, 1 of 6 NFTs in the collection.
